
TY  - JOUR
T1  - Adaptive, Rate-Optimal Hypothesis Testing in Nonparametric IV Models
AU  - Breunig, Christoph
AU  - Chen, Xiaohong
Y1  - 2024/11/01
PY  - 2024
DA  - 2024/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA18602
T2  - Econometrica
